Deemos looked behind him and thought that Aerotaur was going to chase him.
When he seen that Aerotaur was not going to, his heart slows down. He would
never admit it, but if he had staye dany longer, he would have gotten
killed. He runs way ahead of his comrades.

Zeni's eyes open.

Technosis: Oh! I'm so relieved!

Perplex runs up.

Perplex: What happened?

Perplex sees Zeni and faints, knowing something was wrong.

Gramps: He fainted again! I wish that cocky cruel bot didn't run off, I
could have taken him even! He just sneaks up on others from behind, much
like the evil killer back on Cybertron. But it wasn't him.

Zeni: Aerotaur, Land Mine, my back hurts.

Technosis: It's going to be okay, we'll just fix you up and you'll be as
good as new.

Technosis carried Zeni inside of the ship. She examines him.

Technosis: Poor baby, I'll make sure nothing happens to you.

Technosis was acting like a mother...
